&lt;p&gt;Long Meadow Ranch is a family-owned and operated estate dedicated to crafting world-class wine and food through diversified, sustainable, and organic farming. Our integrated agricultural system includes estate vineyards, olive orchards, cattle, and gardens – all nestled in the heart of Napa Valley.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;Farmstead at Long Meadow Ranch&lt;/strong&gt;, we bring our farm to your table. Housed in a former nursery barn, our restaurant celebrates seasonal, ingredient-driven American farmhouse cuisine, curated by Executive Chef Stephen Barber. We proudly serve dishes crafted with our own grass-fed beef, heirloom vegetables, organic eggs, extra virgin olive oil, and award-winning wines – all sourced from our land or neighboring farms.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;inspired and driven Sous Chef&lt;/strong&gt; to join our passionate culinary team. This is more than a job – it’s a chance to be part of a restaurant that truly lives and breathes the farm-to-table philosophy. You&#39;ll work side by side with talented professionals who value sustainability, seasonality, and creativity. If you find joy in precision, take pride in your craft, and are energized by the rhythm of a busy kitchen, this is your place.&lt;/p&gt;
